text: Abay Babes is a 2018 Filipino comedy film written and directed by Don Cuaresma, starring Cristine Reyes, Nathalie Hart, Meg Imperial, Roxanne Barcelo and Kylie Verzosa. The film was produced by Viva Films and it was released in the Philippines on 19 September 2018. ==Cast== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Philippine films Category:Viva Films films
